info.name: RestFull API - Warkop Rumah Seduh
info.description:
API Collection untuk Sistem Pemesanan Warkop Rumah Seduh

## Base URL
- Development: http://localhost:8000
- Production: https://your-domain.com

## Authentication
Menggunakan Laravel Sanctum dengan Bearer Token

## Endpoints Available:
- Authentication (Login, Logout, Me)
- Product Management (CRUD)
- Order Management
- Analytics & Reports

request.description:
Login endpoint untuk mendapatkan authentication token

**Request Body:**
- email (string, required): Email user
- password (string, required): Password user

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "message": "Login berhasil",
  "token": "1|abc123...",
  "user": {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "okan",
    "email": "okan@gmail.com"
  }
}
```

**Error Response (401):**
```json
{
  "message": "Email atau password salah"
}
```

Mendapatkan ringkasan statistik stok

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "total_products": 4,
    "available_products": 4,
    "out_of_stock": 0,
    "low_stock_products": 1,
    "total_stock_value": 2450000
  }
}
```

Update stok produk

**Request Body:**
- action (enum): increase, decrease, set
- quantity (integer): Jumlah
- reason (string, optional): Alasan perubahan

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Stok berhasil diupdate",
  "data": {
    "product_id": 1,
    "product_name": "Cappuccino",
    "old_stock": 50,
    "new_stock": 60,
    "action": "increase",
    "quantity": 10
  }
}
```

Mendapatkan semua produk yang tersedia

**Success Response (200):**
```json
[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Cappuccino",
    "image": "https://example.com/cappuccino.jpg",
    "price": 10000.00,
    "category": "coffee",
    "created_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00.000000Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00.000000Z"
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "name": "Matcha Latte",
    "image": "https://example.com/matcha.jpg",
    "price": 15000.00,
    "category": "non_coffee"
  }
]
```

formdata.description: Optional image file (jpeg, png, jpg, gif, max 2MB)

request.description:
Membuat produk baru (Requires Authentication)

**Headers:**
- Authorization: Bearer {token}

**Form Data:**
- name (string, required): Nama produk
- category (enum, required): coffee, non_coffee, makanan, cemilan
- price (numeric, required): Harga produk
- image (file, optional): Gambar produk (jpeg, png, jpg, gif, max 2MB)

**Success Response (201):**
```json
{
  "message": "Produk berhasil ditambahkan",
  "product": {
    "id": 5,
    "name": "Espresso",
    "category": "coffee",
    "price": 8000,
    "image": "products/abc123.jpg"
  }
}
```

Mendapatkan semua pesanan dengan detail items

**Success Response (200):**
```json
[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "order_id": "ORD-abc123",
    "customer_name": "John Doe",
    "customer_meja": "A1",
    "customer_phone": "081234567890",
    "notes": "Gula sedikit",
    "total_price": 25000.00,
    "fee_platform": 1000.00,
    "total_bayar": 26000.00,
    "payment_status": "sukses",
    "status": "Selesai",
    "payment_method": "midtrans",
    "created_at": "2025-01-01T00:00:00.000000Z",
    "order_items": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "product_name": "Cappuccino",
        "quantity": 2,
        "price": 10000.00,
        "subtotal": 20000.00
      }
    ]
  }
]
```

Mendapatkan detail pesanan berdasarkan ID

**URL Parameters:**
- id (integer): ID pesanan

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "id": 1,
  "order_id": "ORD-abc123",
  "customer_name": "John Doe",
  "customer_meja": "A1",
  "customer_phone": "081234567890",
  "notes": "Gula sedikit",
  "total_price": 25000.00,
  "fee_platform": 1000.00,
  "total_bayar": 26000.00,
  "payment_status": "sukses",
  "status": "Selesai",
  "payment_method": "midtrans",
  "order_items": [...]
}
```

Membuat pesanan cash (langsung dibayar) - Requires Authentication

**Headers:**
- Authorization: Bearer {token}
- Content-Type: application/json

**Request Body:**
- name (string, required): Nama pelanggan
- phone (string, required): Nomor telepon
- customer_meja (string, required): Nomor meja
- note (string, optional): Catatan pesanan
- items (array, required): Array item pesanan
  - name (string, required): Nama produk
  - price (numeric, required): Harga produk
  - quantity (integer, required): Jumlah

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Pesanan berhasil disimpan dan stok telah diupdate.",
  "order": {
    "id": 1,
    "order_id": "INV-1234567890",
    "customer_name": "Jane Smith",
    "customer_meja": "B2",
    "customer_phone": "081987654321",
    "notes": "Tanpa gula",
    "total_price": 38000,
    "fee_platform": 1260,
    "total_bayar": 39260,
    "status": "Selesai",
    "payment_status": "sukses",
    "payment_method": "cash",
    "order_items": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "order_id": 1,
        "product_name": "Cappuccino",
        "quantity": 2,
        "price": 10000,
        "subtotal": 20000
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "order_id": 1,
        "product_name": "Nasi Goreng",
        "quantity": 1,
        "price": 18000,
        "subtotal": 18000
      }
    ]
  },
  "payment_details": {
    "total_order": 38000,
    "fee_platform": 1260,
    "total_bayar": 39260,
    "estimasi_potongan_midtrans": 275,
    "dana_masuk_platform": 38985,
    "owner_terima": 38000,
    "platform_terima": 985
  }
}
```

Update status pembayaran pesanan menjadi sukses

**URL Parameters:**
- orderId (string): ID pesanan (order_id)

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "message": "Status pembayaran berhasil diperbarui menjadi sukses"
}
```

Mendapatkan detail perhitungan fee untuk pesanan tertentu

**URL Parameters:**
- id (integer): ID pesanan

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "total_order": 38000,
  "fee_platform": 1260,
  "total_bayar": 39260,
  "estimasi_potongan_midtrans": 275,
  "dana_masuk_platform": 38985,
  "owner_terima": 38000,
  "platform_terima": 985
}
```

Mendapatkan data pendapatan berdasarkan periode waktu

**Query Parameters:**
- type (string, optional): day, week, month (default: day)
- year (integer, optional): Tahun (default: tahun sekarang)
- month (integer, optional): Bulan (1-12)
- day (integer, optional): Tanggal (1-31)

**Success Response (200):**
```json
[
  {
    "label": "2025-09-01",
    "jumlah": 250000
  },
  {
    "label": "2025-09-02",
    "jumlah": 320000
  }
]
```

Mendapatkan data produk terlaris berdasarkan periode waktu

**Query Parameters:**
- year (integer, optional): Tahun (default: tahun sekarang)
- month (integer, optional): Bulan (1-12)

**Success Response (200):**
```json
[
  {
    "product_name": "Cappuccino",
    "total_terjual": 120
  },
  {
    "product_name": "Nasi Goreng",
    "total_terjual": 85
  }
]
```
